411
00:23:07,968 --> 00:23:10,425
There is no atmosphere
at this altitude.

412
00:23:10,512 --> 00:23:12,298
I don't need you
blacking out on me.

413
00:23:12,389 --> 00:23:13,595
(Door opens)

414
00:23:15,142 --> 00:23:17,929
Hey, your heads-up display has
a built-in guidance system.

415
00:23:19,355 --> 00:23:21,061
Open your chute when the system says,

416
00:23:21,148 --> 00:23:22,809
