419
00:23:26,487 --> 00:23:27,567
Crystal.

420
00:23:38,499 --> 00:23:39,909
(Thunder rumbling)

421
00:23:50,094 --> 00:23:51,880
We got to talk. We need to rethink this.

422
00:23:51,971 --> 00:23:53,256
Out of my way, hunt.

423
00:23:53,347 --> 00:23:55,283
Walker, we've got a problem.
There's a storm. We need to...

424
00:23:55,307 --> 00:23:57,263
- (Air hissing)
- Walker: Enough talk.

