(Gasps)

516
00:32:55,931 --> 00:32:57,467
(Panting)

517
00:33:00,894 --> 00:33:02,259
(Whispers) Shit.

518
00:33:13,573 --> 00:33:15,564
(Glass crunching)

519
00:33:21,164 --> 00:33:24,577
- Can you still make a mask?
- I need a face to make a mask.

520
00:33:24,668 --> 00:33:27,956
Sorry. I was aiming for his chest.

521
00:33:29,506 --> 00:33:31,713
- What are you doing here?
- It's good to see you, too.

522
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:34,337
